'''Mariam Nazarian''' (a.k.a Marie Nazar) is a concert pianist and producer; she is a graduate of the [[Mannes College of Music]] and [[Harvard University]]. Nazarian has performed at [[Carnegie Hall]] (New York),<ref name="cvnc" /><ref name="nytimes" /><ref name="nytimes2" /> [[Symphony Hall, Boston|Symphony Hall]] (Boston), and the [[Saint Petersburg Philharmonia|Grand Philharmonic Hall]] (St. Petersburg, Russia).<ref name=US1 /> She has recorded a commercially released CD of [[Johann Sebastian Bach|J.S. Bach's]] [[Goldberg Variations]].<ref name="cvnc" />
